T02TD3506E:155a-1: sarba aartha s'a dh'a n+ya a'arya bra sanna t'a r'a s'a dha ni /
T02TD3506E:155a-3: don thams cad grub pa rab tu sbyin pa'i 'phags ma sgrol ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3506E:155a-4: 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3506E:155a-5: sngon ma'i rim pa rab tu sbyor bas bha ga'i dbus su zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la lha mo sgrol ma chen mo gser gyi mdog lta bu 'jigs pa chen mo zhal brgyad pa /
T02TD3506E:155a-7: phyag bcu drug gis rnam par brgyan pa /
T02TD3506E:155a-8: dbu skra kham pa gyen du brdzes pa /
T02TD3506E:155a-9: mgo bo rlon pa'i phreng ba brgya phyed kyis do shal byas pa /
T02TD3506E:155a-10: 'gro ba rnams skyob pa'i stobs chen mo zhabs g-yas brkyang ba dang ldan pa /
T02TD3506E:155a-11: bzhad cing lang cho gzhon nu la sna tshogs pa'i gos kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3506E:155a-13: g-yas kyi gnyis pa ni nag po /
T02TD3506E:155a-15: bzhi pa ni nam mkha' lta bu sngon po'o //
T02TD3506E:155a-16: g-yon pa ni kunda lta bu /
T02TD3506E:155a-18: gsum pa ni nam mkha' lta bu sngon po /
T02TD3506E:155a-19: steng ni du ba'i mdog lta bu 'jigs pa chen mo'o //
T02TD3506E:155a-20: zhal dbus ma rnam par gtsigs pa'o //
T02TD3506E:155a-21: phyag g-yas pa rnams na ral gri dang /
T02TD3506E:155a-23: rdo rje dang lcags kyu dang /
T02TD3506E:155b-0: g-yon gyi @155b phyag rnams na zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub dang /
T02TD3506E:155b-4: rdo rje dang bcas pa'i zhags pa dang /
T02TD3506E:155b-8: sna tshogs padma dang zla ba la bzhugs pa //
T02TD3506E:155b-9: nyi ma'i 'od kyis rnam par brgyan pa /
T02TD3506E:155b-10: zhabs g-yon pas dbang po dang /
T02TD3506E:155b-11: zhabs gnyis kyi dbus su drag po dang /
T02TD3506E:155b-14: sgrib pa thams cad rnam par 'joms pa /
T02TD3506E:155b-15: rnal 'byor pas bsgoms pas myur du dngos grub rnams thob par 'gyur ro //
T02TD3506E:155b-16: bzlas pa'i sngags ni aom pra sanna t'a ree aa mri te /
T02TD3506E:155b-17: aa mri ta mu khe aa mri ta lo tsa ne sarb'artha s'a dha ni sarba satva ba sham ka ri h'um h'um phat sv'ah'a /
T02TD3506E:155b-18: zhes pa ni don thams cad rab tu grub pa sbyin pa'i 'phags ma sgrol ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
